"You are fully liable for any negative balance on your Stripe Issuing "
"account.\n"
"                    Repayment is due immediately upon notice."
msgstr ""
"Eres totalmente responsable de cualquier saldo negativo en tu cuenta de "
"Stripe Issuing.\n"
"                    El reembolso deberá efectuarse inmediatamente tras la "
"notificación."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/static/src/components/open_card_receive_terms.xml:0
msgid ""
"You are responsible for all transactions made with your card,\n"
"                    including unauthorized charges unless covered by law or "
"Stripe’s policy."
msgstr ""
"Eres responsable de todas las transacciones realizadas con tu tarjeta,\n"
"                    incluidos los cargos no autorizados, salvo que estén "
"cubiertos por la ley o por la política de Stripe."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "You can't change the card type once the card has been created."
msgstr "No se puede cambiar el tipo de tarjeta una vez que se ha creado."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "You can't change the delivery address once the card has been shipped."
msgstr ""
"No se puede cambiar la dirección de entrega una vez que la tarjeta ha sido "
"enviada."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"You can't change the employee of an active card. Please create a new card "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"No se puede cambiar el empleado de una tarjeta activa; crea una nueva "
"tarjeta."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"You can't delete a card that already exists for Stripe, please block it "
"instead"
msgstr ""
"No puedes eliminar una tarjeta que ya existe en Stripe, por favor, bloquéala"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
