"You cannot delete an expense that was created from a Stripe card transaction."
msgstr ""
"No se puede eliminar un gasto creado a partir de una transacción con tarjeta "
"Stripe."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot duplicate an expense that was created from a Stripe card "
"transaction."
msgstr ""
"No se puede duplicar un gasto creado a partir de una transacción con tarjeta "
"Stripe."

